rost", "Karlas Kabale", "Angels in the snow", "A Christmas Carol", "A dogwalker's christmas tale", "Angels of christmas", "Once upon a holiday", "Holiday in handcuffs", "Anywhere but home", "The spirit of christmas", "Mirakel", "Julebordet", "Sykt lykkelig", "Family man"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "b3b6fcde0cd059b392fadf6105e7d544f07eda14aa379581d7dcac2b1a27b63d"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-01-18T13:13:27.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "De koselige klassiske julefilmene har blitt pakket opp i god tid f\u00f8r jul p\u00e5 str\u00f8mmetjenesten."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article13885278.ece/b2tdkr/ALTERNATES/w980-default/HOME6.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/a0d7223be592ddba08472cd56dad81f0c6c1d554.jpg?597e1cc6"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Jul p\u00e5 Netflix -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "a0d7223be592ddba08472cd56dad81f0c6c1d554"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["anmeldelser", "det skjer", "film", "musikk", "tv", "museum", "scene", "spill"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "anmeldelser,det skjer,film,musikk,tv,museum,scene,spill"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "buddy"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["jul", "on 34th street", "on 34th", "hysterisk morsom", "of christmas", "film", "christmas", "34th street"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["turbo man", "oscar", "white christmas", "br\u00f8drene", "back", "joe pesci og daniel stern", "hjelp", "forest gump", "luke wilson og paul schneider", "michael cera og rashida jones", "white cristmas", "dermot mulroney", "kevin", "miley cyrus", "manhatten", "wonderland", "richard at